Scenario: Create new game room
  Given Alice is on the multiplayer start page
  When Alice clicks "Create Game"
  And Alice selects 4 players
  And Alice chooses "Terran Alliance" faction
  Then a unique room code is generated
  And Alice is designated as the host
  And the lobby shows "1/4 players"
  And Alice sees the room code displayed prominently

Scenario: Join existing game room
  Given Bob has a valid room code from Alice
  When Bob enters the room code on the start page
  And Bob clicks "Join Game"
  Then Bob joins Alice's game room
  And the lobby shows "2/4 players"
  And both Alice and Bob see each other in the player list
  And Bob can select a faction different from Alice's

Scenario: Game starts when all players ready
  Given a 4-player game room with 4 joined players
  And all players have selected different factions
  When all players mark themselves as ready
  Then the game transitions from lobby to game board
  And each player sees their home sector on the galaxy board
  And the turn order is determined and displayed
  And the first player's action phase begins

Scenario: Prevent game start with incomplete lobby
  Given a 4-player game room with only 2 joined players
  When the host attempts to start the game
  Then the game does not start
  And an error message displays "Waiting for 2 more players"
  And the lobby remains active

Scenario: Host can kick players from lobby
  Given Alice is the host of a 4-player game
  And Bob has joined the lobby
  When Alice clicks "Kick" next to Bob's name
  Then Bob is removed from the lobby
  And Bob sees a message "You were removed from the game"
  And the lobby shows "1/4 players" again
